  "Name": {
    "English": "SPEWING VENTS",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "喷口",
    "TraditionalChinese": "噴射口"
  },
  "NameLower": {
    "English": "Spewing Vents",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "喷口",
    "TraditionalChinese": "噴射口"
  },
  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Fused Organic Technology",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "有机融合技术",
    "TraditionalChinese": "融合有機科技"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A mess of sacs and sphincters, these vents generate and expel globules of plasma. When fused to the weapon systems of the ship, these are super-heated and then expelled at high-pressure.<br><br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to ask if the ship would direct its vents towards the current target.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一团囊和括约肌，这些喷口产生并排出等离子体球。当熔合到飞船的武器系统上时，这些系统会过热，然后在高压下被排出。<br><br>按<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>询问飞船是否会将喷口对准当前目标。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "噴射口由大量囊袋和括約肌組成，可以分泌並排出滴狀電漿。和太空船的武器系統融合後，會過熱噴射出高壓電漿。<br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 詢問太空船願不願意將噴射口瞄準目前的目標。"
  },
  "Teach": true,
  "HintStart": "",
  "HintEnd": {
    "English": "Switch Weapon Mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span><br>Fire Weapons with <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切换武器模式<br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 用武器开火",
    "TencentChinese": "按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切换武器模式<br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 用武器开火",
    "TraditionalChinese": "按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切換武器模式<br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 發射武器"
  },
